                           <locus target="#98v">f. 98v</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#98v">98v</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘ&lt;...&gt;</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#98v">98v</locus>: This book is of &lt;…&gt;
                              (144v)</quote> - The note is written in the same hand as the main
                           text. The personal name was scratched out but its second part might be
                           ʾIyasus. - An identical ownership note at the end of Text II, <locus target="#144r">144r</locus>
                           <note>. </note>
                        </item>
